# 📂 Dataset Documentation: Accident Detection from CCTV Footage

## 📌 Overview
This dataset is designed for **binary image classification** to detect road accidents from CCTV footage.

- **Task Type:** Image Classification  
- **Classes:** 2 (Accident, Non-Accident)  
- **Domain:** Computer Vision / Intelligent Transportation Systems  

---

## 📊 Dataset Distribution

| Category       | Train | Validation | Test | Total |
|----------------|------:|-----------:|-----:|------:|
| Accident       | 369   | 46         | 47   | 462   |
| Non-Accident   | 422   | 52         | 54   | 528   |
| **Total**      | 791   | 98         | 101  | 990   |

